'''Steve John Shepherd''' is an actor who was credited for portraying "Naboo Lieutenant" in the [[2002]] [[prequel trilogy]] film [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']].<ref name="AOTC">{{Film|II}}</ref> In [[Star Wars Legends|''Star Wars'' Legends]], the character was later identified as [[Theomet Danlé/Legends|Theomet Danlé]] in the [[Databank (original)|Databank]],<ref name="db">{{DB|character|theometdanle|Danlé, Theomet}}</ref> a name that was retained in [[canon]].<ref name="build">{{BuildFalconCite|55|Starship Fact File}} {{1stID|Theomet Danlé}}</ref>

